Middle school can be tough, huh?

00:18:02.380 --> 00:18:05.830
So you stopped going to school
and started fooling around at night.

00:18:06.210 --> 00:18:09.960
Well, I know I shouldn't be doing this kind of thing.

00:18:11.500 --> 00:18:13.040
Tell me, boy.

00:18:13.040 --> 00:18:15.500
How does your first night out feel?

00:18:15.960 --> 00:18:19.830
What do you think now that you've
taken a step outside the norm?

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:28.290
This place is the furthest you can hope to get
from all those things you think are a pain.

00:18:28.630 --> 00:18:32.500
It'd be a waste if you didn't keep this kind of thing up.

00:18:39.960 --> 00:18:41.710
<i>I was getting by just fine...</i>

00:18:42.500 --> 00:18:43.710
<i>I think.</i>

00:18:44.040 --> 00:18:46.290
<i>At least, I tried to do the right thing...</i>

00:18:47.040 --> 00:18:50.380
<i>because there was nothing
I wanted to do or wanted to be.</i>

00:18:51.710 --> 00:18:53.130
Who cares?

00:18:53.420 --> 00:18:55.500
School's boring, right?

00:18:57.960 --> 00:19:01.790
Stay up until you feel satisfied about your day.

00:19:02.290 --> 00:19:04.880
That's not a bad way to live.

00:19:07.710 --> 00:19:09.670
So yeah, do me a favor and-

00:19:09.670 --> 00:19:10.670
Miss Vampire!

00:19:10.670 --> 00:19:11.880
Huh? Y-yeah?!

00:19:11.880 --> 00:19:13.080
