00:19:14.630 --> 00:19:17.130
Turn me into a vampire!

00:19:21.130 --> 00:19:22.790
H-hold up a sec.

00:19:22.790 --> 00:19:24.000
What?

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:28.580
L-like I said, a person has to fulfill certain conditions
in order to become a vampire-

00:19:28.580 --> 00:19:29.960
I know that!

00:19:29.960 --> 00:19:30.670
They need to fall in love with a vampire.

00:19:30.670 --> 00:19:32.750
Ah! Don't, it's embarrassing!
They need to fall in love with a vampire.<b></b>

00:19:33.380 --> 00:19:35.830
I'd probably never take that leap.

00:19:36.380 --> 00:19:40.710
I know I'll just go back to my old life
and spend my days in boredom.

00:19:41.670 --> 00:19:43.210
But now I've seen it...

00:19:43.540 --> 00:19:44.750
the night...

00:19:45.250 --> 00:19:47.130
It's the first time I've wanted to be something.

00:19:47.710 --> 00:19:49.380
I don't want to dismiss this feeling!

00:19:49.750 --> 00:19:52.580
So please, let me fall in love with you!

00:19:57.580 --> 00:19:59.250
You're being ridiculous.

00:20:00.130 --> 00:20:02.670
It's my policy to not create offspring, y'know.

00:20:04.290 --> 00:20:08.210
Just so you know, I'm not going to do anything.

00:20:08.500 --> 00:20:11.130
I'm just gonna suck your blood
like the vampire that I am.

00:20:11.380 --> 00:20:13.710
If you wanna fall in love, go ahead.

00:20:15.420 --> 00:20:17.000
I'm Nazuna Nanakusa.

00:20:17.000 --> 00:20:18.210
You?

00:20:19.080 --> 00:20:20.500
Ko Yamori.

00:20:23.250 --> 00:20:26.750
Do you know when human blood tastes best?

00:20:28.080 --> 00:20:29.500
At night.

00:20:29.500 --> 00:20:33.750
Especially right before a person falls asleep
to the moment that they do.

00:20:34.080 --> 00:20:37.790
That's because the blood is infused with night.

00:20:38.210 --> 00:20:40.960
Um, why the roof?

00:20:40.960 --> 00:20:43.790
Because we're closer to the moon, obviously.

00:20:43.790 --> 00:20:45.000
What?

00:20:45.000 --> 00:20:46.920
If you think about the distance to the moon,

00:20:46.920 --> 00:20:49.830
the difference between the ground
and the roof is negligible.

00:20:50.420 --> 00:20:55.290
That's why I want to infuse more night in you, boy.

00:20:55.290 --> 00:20:57.040
You mean I need to stay up late?

00:20:57.580 --> 00:21:00.130
Well, I plan on that anyway.

00:21:00.130 --> 00:21:06.420
That too, of course, but in order to infuse blood
with night - in other words, to stay up late -

00:21:06.420 --> 00:21:09.000
you can't just stay awake.

00:21:09.750 --> 00:21:11.630
But you wouldn't know what I mean.

00:21:12.250 --> 00:21:13.250
Huh?

00:21:13.670 --> 00:21:15.630
So I'll teach you...

00:21:15.830 --> 00:21:17.880
what it means to enjoy the night.

00:21:19.920 --> 00:21:20.710
I'm gonna die!

00:21:20.710 --> 00:21:21.710
No, you won't.
I'm gonna die!<b></b>

00:21:28.210 --> 00:21:30.040
The night is for fooling around.

00:21:30.460 --> 00:21:32.630
Let's have some fun, boy.

00:21:34.210 --> 00:21:36.500
Hang on tight.

00:22:24.920 --> 00:22:26.710
What do you think, boy?

00:22:27.000 --> 00:22:28.460
How do you feel?

00:22:46.130 --> 00:22:47.420
Awesome.

00:22:48.500 --> 00:22:49.710
Isn't it?

